The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Youhana embraces Islam

Islamabad: Pakistan cricket star Yusuf Youhana, who was the only Christian in the team, has converted to Islam. 

The conversion took place with members of a tableeghi jamaat present with him in Mecca, where he and his family said the kalma and later performed umra, a cricketer was quoted as saying by a Pakistani newspaper on Saturday. 

Youhana and his family have also been issued certificates in the holy place confirming their Muslim status which allowed them to perform umra, he said. 

